name: Fish And Chips (elsen0xcc)
description:
Two fishes wrestle to be the last one standing. Two-player game.

Bubble and Bububble are living a quiet life in their aquarium,
One day, the family adopts Chips, a cat that loooooves fish.

Who will survive?

In this two players game,
each player tries to kick the other out of the screen and be the last one standing.
